{"tid":1451131,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［重要］如果大家再搞塞鐵","createTime":"2019-08-11T18:24:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T19:00:06.000Z","uid":35831,"like":15,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"da6003a5701b8f36d140a49fcdb3dcd6bf361298","tid":1451131,"uid":35831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:24:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">麻煩唔好剩係塞一日半日</span></strong></span><br />\n塞一日半日其實無意思，塞完聽日又繼續返工，有乜用<br />\n去到呢個政府蠻不講理嘅時代，梗係要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">持續嘅抗爭，一塞塞一個禮拜啦</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n最少事件唔會令好多人受傷，最多都係返唔到工<br />\n<br />\n最後，我想講<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不分化，不篤灰，不割蓆（警犬朋友另計，請篤灰，請割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"36e5b3cb5de03c33936cea71debd753bf06063ec","tid":1451131,"uid":263577,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:24:30.000Z","msg":"入機場"},{"pid":"e5c24bea0562c68786e3380d0a3b9f6a5ff46905","tid":1451131,"uid":35831,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"36e5b3cb5de03c33936cea71debd753bf06063ec","tid":1451131,"uid":263577,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:24:30.000Z","msg":"入機場"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:25:48.000Z","msg":"認同"},{"pid":"453825fa1cf7fe4bf909d4ed2df8c219b4f7d5e0","tid":1451131,"uid":103476,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:26:47.000Z","msg":"非常重要，借位一用<br />\n<br />\n致所有比狗打而想反抗嘅前線<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1448193\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1448193</a>"},{"pid":"247289067c5038e5cd7eca819594ded40c7446ec","tid":1451131,"uid":35831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:26:48.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"74740ff4ca8aef7dcdbf17151dacd53b721dfb77","tid":1451131,"uid":98842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:27:06.000Z","msg":"一人一Post狂洗連登 [時事台]<br />\n唔該你出一份力，肯出post，聽日就係人都知入機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n標題：「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\nTG群組，不停轉發出去，勢要討回雙眼，嬲到火屎呀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n百萬人入機場，機場自然停<br />\n百萬人入機場，機場自然停<br />\n百萬人入機場，機場自然停<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大群好多人入緊：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=926QiOG7cNu1sWdYPFF%2FaNqUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=60e43e66\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n睇消息去實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=926QiOG7cNu1sWdYPFF%2FaNqUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=bbdfd32b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a><br />\n---------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n不要說推<br />\n試著說812機場見"},{"pid":"b37e95f0ed376bce38955bf3732d0ed389dc5564","tid":1451131,"uid":44298,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:27:10.000Z","msg":"唔好塞，唔好去吸毒氣咁on9"},{"pid":"49c7135af9e99b56015a5ef36ee91482bb16f64e","tid":1451131,"uid":195350,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:27:15.000Z","msg":"唔建議"},{"pid":"593b2dca5a1b03b9839f7f9ea32bedf8e555ac03","tid":1451131,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:27:29.000Z","msg":"塞死同路返工人  廢老唔洗返工嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />諗清楚啦"},{"pid":"75d9c5edef9ed81381428584276fd40d4ce7a3fe","tid":1451131,"uid":73358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit